results.description:
Everyone has a set of ideas about how women should dress, behave, and present themselves. A woman with short hair is seen as rebellious and not the ‘wife type’, while the one with long hair is perceived as the ‘traditional type’. Though the world loves to stereotype women, SkinKraft believes every woman is 'her own type'. 

SkinKraft, India’s first customized personal care brand, offers different skincare and haircare products for every woman's skin type and hair type. This is done after a complete analysis of your skin and hair through an online questionnaire. You just have to take up the SkinID or HairID quiz available on SkinKraft's website. Based on the answers provided by you, SkinKraft customizes skincare and haircare solutions, which target your main concern areas. 

SkinKraft products have been formulated by a top team of dermatologists and scientists after several hours of research. The products are 100% safe to use and free of any harsh chemicals. 

Try SkinKraft’s customized skincare products by taking up the SkinID quiz at https://skinkraft.com/pages/spq?utm_s...​ and experience the change!
